Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.44,0:00:04.78,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As times change,\Ndifficult cases grow in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:06.88,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's case is in a mountain lodge in a blizzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:08.85,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The murder victim doesn't stay quiet, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:10.75,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:13.09,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:15.55,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? You're not going to ski, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm taking in this nice, cloudless sky first...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the grandeur of this snowy white landscape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn. I knew I shouldn't have come...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:11.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! You lost the key to the rental cabin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez! It's all thanks to you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess all we can do is call the manager to bring a duplicate key.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:22.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any phone booths around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that cabin is still under construction,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the ski bus already left...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing nearby is that one lodge up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me, ask help from some upstart with a lodge there? Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No choice! We'll open it by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- No, don't!\N- Stop, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say! Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! It is Kogoro Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:52.79,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Masashi Oyama (53)\NToto University Medical Professor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I always read about your brilliant work in the newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a magnificent lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such an elegant color and design!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:03.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who was talking about rich upstarts just a minute ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I haven't heard your names yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Conan Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.\NWe're watching him for a friend of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:17.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This lion-shaped door decoration is superb, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was hoping for a horse,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I guess that was asking too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's true. Horses would be better than lions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's not what I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Oyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Nakahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:42.26,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kaori Nakahara (30)\NToto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What took you so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's been waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are these folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, some friends I ran into just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're all doctors at the same university?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep! We're all assistants for Dr. Oyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:01.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctors are very factional, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:05.62,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tomoyasu Kanazawa (48)\NToto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been studying under the doctor for dozens of years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I transferred here three years ago from some future-less professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:13.87,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ginji Tobita (31)\NToto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad to be where I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:19.75,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kaho Ezumi (30)\NToto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The essay he presented the other day was wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, "Gene Therapy as Treatment for Cancer of the Large Intestine"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The whole medical school is praising his essay right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come now, with my brains, it was a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I forgot to buy snacks to go with our drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go pick some up at the shop at the bottom of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you get some chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dried cuttlefish for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have a salad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Here, write it all down so I know what to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The convenience store closes before 10:00, so hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What time is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,8:58...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A TV show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's addicted to a melodrama that gets 30% ratings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I watch that show, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where are you off to, Dr. Tobita?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Night skiing. I haven't gotten my fix yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should be back by around 11:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll take a nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,relaxing bath until the snacks arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, did you call the cabin manager about our key?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:57.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all right! You can stay the night here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:06:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your father can't exactly leave in his state...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to throw out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! Tsutomu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to, Mitsue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. We can never be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, please! Forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why can't we be together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must've been rough with the sudden blizzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tobita!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, can't possibly night ski with that blizzard out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That warms me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, are we drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was your bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? I had asked for a salad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, they were sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there was no ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who asked for ice cream in this weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was Dr. Oyama? He does love ice cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His TV drama ended at 10:00,\Nso where could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Oyama always tapes the show
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and replays the best scenes afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:35.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn you... This was your original intent all along...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But you won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:42.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The great detective, Kogoro Mouri, is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:47.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sure that he, if anyone, will get this message!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Kogoro Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy always in the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! My dad's a detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's past 11:00 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he's taking a bit too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go see what's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? He's that famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks sure can be deceiving...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Oyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too late. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, let's untie his ropes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it if you don't mess up the murder scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! They can't get police cars
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or an ambulance here in this blizzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That so? Then I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I, the great Kogoro Mouri, will have to take charge here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:51.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're still so drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll ask just to be safe—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no one's touched anything in the room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing aside from Dr. Oyama's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found him first, Nakahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I assume the same goes for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. I saw him covered in blood
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and fell down in the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there anything of value in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He does have a safe in the cabinet to the right of the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all scratched up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know what's inside this safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cash, I assume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He always carried large sums of money with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I guess they were after money...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's with this blood trail?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:42.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's almost as if he crawled to the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:45.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And why is he sitting formally?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:50.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The blood on the table stops cleanly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:53.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah. The tablecloth slipped off...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:57.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Marks from the bloodied rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:10:02.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could this be a dying message from Dr. Oyama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:08.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they used tape on the window to muffle the sound, then snuck in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were even nice enough to leave footprints outside the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I've got this figured out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No "hmmms"! Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate to ask, but could you examine him for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As doctors, you're more qualified than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even his beloved gold watch is covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quit joking around at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I estimate his time of death to be between 9:30 and 10:00 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So it was during his TV drama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are countless cuts all over his body,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it appears he died of suffocation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after having both lungs punctured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suffocation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Basically, with holes in his lungs,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he couldn't hold air to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably suffered terribly for 10 or 15 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who on earth would do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was most likely done for monetary gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After breaking in through the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the killer attacked and tied up\NDr. Oyama, who was watching TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then demanded the safe combination, but didn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enraged, the culprit stabbed Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and fled back out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:42.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ugh, talk about dense...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! This man has a cool watch! It's all sparkly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, he was tied up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he was super lucky the killer didn't take his gold watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:12:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How odd for someone after money to overlook a watch like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that the killer must be pretty stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you think the killer must've been gutsy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? Look at the footprints outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They come straight to this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was me, I'd be afraid someone else was in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and would sneak around and peek in before going inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scratching the safe and tying Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} up was camouflage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,meant to make it look like this was about money...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer knew Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would be watching TV alone then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, one of you four is the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's hear each of your alibis between 9:30 and 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:12.91,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kaori Nakahara (30)\NToto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left at 9:00 and returned at around 9:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only snacks that were sold out were salad and ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you could've finished sooner if you rushed in your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It takes over 40 minutes round-trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think I'm lying, you can try it with my car!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:35.81,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ginji Tobita (31)\NToto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went night skiing, a ski slope also 40 minutes round-trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have proof of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This lift ticket has today's date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, it even has the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:49.57,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kaho Ezumi (30)\NToto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cleaned up and washed things with Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She only left for 2 or 3 minutes to throw out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:58.25,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tomoyasu Kanazawa (48)\NToto University Medical Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was taking a bath from 9:30 until shortly after 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:04.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's one other person besides Kanazawa{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} with a flimsy alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:09.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}B-Blood stains?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:12.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? But why isn't there any blood on the sofa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:16.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did someone put it here after the blood dried?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:20.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute. The blood-smeared tablecloth... Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:25.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It matches perfectly! This lighter was sitting here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:28.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:31.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it, this afternoon, Oyama{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was hoping for a horse, but I guess that was asking too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:39.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was when he asked me and Ran our names...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:43.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! A horse! That's what he meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:45.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This really is Oyama{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s dying message!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:47.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It explains his formal way of sitting,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:51.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the bloody lighter on the sofa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:55.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And just as his dying message says,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:58.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the killer was that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister. There's something weird on the sofa—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, you damn kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he's drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! I ain't drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured it all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! What, now?! What did you figure out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer. I just now figured out\Nwho stabbed Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:38.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First is Tobita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who went night skiing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have made up a fake story\Nthat could be easily verified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next is you, Ezumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You only left Ran and Conan for 2 or 3 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not enough time to have killed Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which only leaves Kanazawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Nakahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} without alibis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:59.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on! I bought the snacks that everyone asked—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how much did it all cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:08.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you didn't forget. You don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you bought large amounts of all kinds of snacks in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bought them this afternoon when you bought the food for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the murder, you took everyone's orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then pretended to leave in your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then stopped somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and pulled out the snacks they ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:38.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you had an alibi,\Nyou went and murdered Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid; you have no proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you know yourself that there's proof
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in this room that you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:52.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a look at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood ends cleanly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it seem like something was on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tablecloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:17:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please put it on the table so that it matches with the blood stains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:11.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s dying message.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is this a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think back. Oyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} died while sitting formally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:24.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,Masashi Oyama
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:24.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tomoyasu Kanazawa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:24.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ginji Tobita
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:24.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kaho Ezumi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:24.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kaori Nakahara
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should start to become clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each of your names includes characters used in shogi (Japanese chess).
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:27.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,Masashi Oyama
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:27.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tomoyasu Kanazawa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:27.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ginji Tobita
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:27.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kaho Ezumi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:27.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kaori Nakahara
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Shogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Dr. Oyama always said how a horse would make the full set.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. You make up all the pieces but a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran. Take the lighter on the sofa and put it on the tablecloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one place the blood on the lighter matches the tablecloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:58.49,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Kaori"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. That is a lance's starting position.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a dying message that gives your name, Kaori Nakahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know that before putting the tablecloth on the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That square is the only one with long blood trails.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it was on the very edge of the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just coincidentally turned out that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why did you move it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you who tossed the tablecloth aside, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! It must've happened when\Nthe killer and Dr. Oyama struggled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. The blood on the table ends cleanly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the sofa the bloody lighter was on has no blood at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is proof that someone moved it after the blood dried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:19:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the killer must've returned to the scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,noticed the message, and tossed it aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong, Kaori Nakahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your undoing was that you noticed the message after you screamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one other thing—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you said they were out of salad and ice cream,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but setting aside the salad, selling out of ice cream is—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! I killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you do that to him, Kaori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got along so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he was like a father to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I couldn't forgive him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe he'd steal my paper from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Paper? You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Gene Therapy as Treatment for Cancer of the Large Intestine"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! He stole it from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I had spent six whole years pouring my life into that essay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the paper I wrote for my late father's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father died of large intestinal cancer when I was very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason I became a doctor devoted to large intestinal cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was to prevent any more cases like my father's!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet, after he stole the paper I had finally completed, that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:26.07,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:31.47,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nobody'll listen to you if you said you wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:36.38,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But society will pay attention if a famous professor makes it public!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:41.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sure your father would be happier that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was then that I devised this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to kill the man who stomped on my feelings for my father
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by puncturing his lungs,\None of the worst ways to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:58.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never once imagined\Nhe would leave a dying message
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,during those 10 to 15 minutes of agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was one mistake in your theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had predicted the ice cream and salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were sold out of salad, but I did buy ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:18.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:21.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It melted inside the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had everyone's snacks ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and told myself, "OK, time to kill him."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then I suddenly thought back to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After spacing out for a while, the car's heater had melted it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think his ice cream would trip me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:43.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:20.48,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Dying messages. Sometimes, they're expressed in unusual ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got your angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your silver general is going to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Now it's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:36.83,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sometimes, when you change your perspective of something ordinary...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.50,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Look from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.70,0:23:38.71,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Idiot"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.32,0:23:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dead in the pool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He drowned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because you've been in water before
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.49,0:23:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,doesn't make you an expert!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.30,0:23:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you painted what you saw from here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:05.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is! Ah, now I get it! That person was the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this was a murder made to look like an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.69,0:24:14.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.70,0:24:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Cap
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.91,0:24:21.79,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, it's an "in" sports club!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.79,0:24:23.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, Genta! Run it one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.65,0:24:24.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I can't do any more.
